So, just in preparing for this
lecture, on an impulse, I got

01:09:04.340 --> 01:09:05.700
on to Google.

01:09:05.700 --> 01:09:10.740
And I searched on
vacation loans.

01:09:10.740 --> 01:09:16.600
I found 1.6 million websites
that were encouraging you to

01:09:16.600 --> 01:09:20.460
take out a loan to
go on a vacation.

01:09:20.460 --> 01:09:24.040
Now, is that socially
conscious?

01:09:24.040 --> 01:09:25.880
I was wondering about that.

01:09:25.880 --> 01:09:29.330
Is it ever right to borrow money
to go on a vacation?

01:09:29.330 --> 01:09:31.720
I mean, I've thought about it.

01:09:31.720 --> 01:09:35.600
And then I remembered, Franco
Modigliani, who was one of the

01:09:35.600 --> 01:09:38.420
